'''Deliverer's Robe of Legacy''' is a [[Relic]] in the set [[World-Remaking Deliverer]].

==Description==
Aquila's dark clouds rumbled with rage,<br />the hero of deliverance trod upon a bridge of rainbows, and struck down the once untouchable sky.

Standing beside the hero of deliverance were the companions who had faced life and death together with {{MC|f=her|m=him}}.<br />''"Losses are a constant on the Flame-Chase journey, among which even life itself holds little value."''<br />Upon hearing these words, the resolute Deliverer calmly replied:<br />''"I have long understood your determination, and even after tens of thousands of times, I will never betray it."''

On the way to the Era Nova ceremony, the Deliverer bid farewell to {{MC|f=her|m=his}} comrades one by one, comrades who would defend their way back.<br />''"That is an expedition and saga that lasted over a millennium,''<br />''a story entrusted to us by countless predecessors, one that must conclude here today."''<br />The last partner donned their cloak on the Deliverer's shoulder guards, then turned to countless foes.<br />It was a symbol of them fighting together. It was entrusted to them, and it was a legacy.

''"If you can hear me, Talanton... Such a heroic sacrifice deserves a better tomorrow."''<br />''"Therefore, we cast even ourselves into the flame&mdash;"''<br />''"only to inscribe the opening stroke in the poem of creation."''

Under Kephale's gentle gaze, the Deliverer shall recreate the world with everyone's wishes...

